data.description: Extended family or income opportunity. 2 Homes for the price of one ! There is room for everything you have ever collected plus the kids, in-laws  and assorted cousins in this fine Leominster  Rd home. You will be delighted by the hardwood floors and bright rooms flooded with natural light as well as the many amenities for gracious living. This home offers a large corner lot, in-law set up and is still close to all your amenities . See mls 71517949 for addt'l info and pics
